Function parameters start with _
All indentation should be done with tabs converted to spaces
Pass parameters padded with spaces
No camel-case/hungarian in variable/object names
All class/struct names to use CamelCase
Individual tokens to be space padded in expressions (including brackets)
No wildcard imports


Sample code-

Class MyClass
    def func( self, _param1, _param2, _param3, _param4 ):
        a       = _param1 - 5
        bb      = _param2 - 5
        ccc     = _param3 - 5
        dddd    = _param4 - 5

        sum     = ( a * 1 + bb * 2 + ccc * 3 + dddd * 4 )
        lst     = [1, 2]

my_object = MyClass()
print( my_object.func( 1, 2, 3, 4 ) )
